         <div style="flex-basis:100%;"><h2 style="padding-bottom: 0;padding-top:5px;">Brand Building</h2>
                 <p style="padding-top: 0px;"><b>Cause Related Marketing (CRM)</b>
                   When you integrate your marketing efforts with a cause, you not only help create social impact but also build incredible goodwill for your brand. Partnering with HandsOfHope for a cause-related marketing campaign will help you drive purchase behaviour and meet your business objectives – all the while contributing to a really good cause!<br>
         <b>Event Sponsorships & Participation
         </b>HandsOfHope organizes several events (marathons, cyclothons, walkathons and soccer tournaments etc.) across the year to raise awareness for the elderly and disabled’s rights. You can come on board as one of the event sponsors to support the cause and get visibility for your brand or pledge a fixed amount to include a set number of your employees as participants.. 
                   <br><b>Donation Boxes  
                   </b>You can enable HandsOfHope to place physical/digital donation boxes at your office premises or retail outlets to help your employees/customers contribute to the cause. These will be co-branded and thus reflect your association with the cause for the elderly and disabled’s rights.</p></div>
        </div>
          <div style="display: flex;">

            <div style="flex-basis:100%;"><h2 style="padding-bottom: 0;">Corporate Social Responsibility</h2>
                    <p><b>Adopt A Project</b>
                        HandsOfHope works with 72 local projects across 5 states in the areas of education, health, nutrition, safety and protection as well as participation. You can adopt one or more of our projects that fit your CSR needs in terms of geographical location and area of intervention. HandsOfHope will be responsible for monitoring the program, providing programmatic direction and technical expertise to project staff and sending project impact reports periodically.<br>
            <b>Corporate Donations
            </b>You can make a lump sum donation towards a specific cause that your company would like to support. From education,malnutrition, to healthcare and gender inequality – you have a wide array of causes to choose from since HandsOfHope works on all areas of the elderly and disabled’s rights. Your donation would be directed towards HandsOfHope’s programs which address your preferred cause.</p></div>
